author: Fextralife
description:
Silksong 10 Must-Know Gameplay Tips & Tricks - Hollow Knight Silksong Beginner Guide
In this Hollow Knight Silksong video, we're going to be going over 10 tips and tricks to begin your journey. In my experience, Silksong has definitely been a harder game from the get go compared to it's predecessor, Hollow Knight. So there've been a lot of new mechanics that I needed to learn to take advantage of, as well as old tops that I relearned to make my playthrough go much smoother.
